</ref>，基于Jim Flanagan的Search Referral Zeitgeist，一个分析整理网站参考日志（[[HTTP_referrer|HTTP referrer]]）的可视化应用实现。<ref>A copy of Jim Flanagan's Search Referral Zeitgeist was [https://web.archive.org/web/20041204231120/http://twiki.tensegrity.net/bin/view/Main/SearchReferralZeitgeist available at archive.org] but has since been blocked. In the comments of a [http://www.37signals.com/svn/archives/000937.php blog entry] {{Wayback|url=http://www.37signals.com/svn/archives/000937.php |date=20060426191534 }}, a user identified as Steve Minutillo attribute the idea to  Jim Flanagan, stating that Flanagan's site had such displays in 2002.</ref>[[Del.icio.us|Del.icio.us]]和[[Technorati|Technorati]]等网站也为标签云的普及起了推动作用。

